    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/fce34db061518d4f1627543d3be47f2d.poster.avif?t=1741367325\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/fce34db061518d4f1627543d3be47f2d.webm?t=1741367325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/fce34db061518d4f1627543d3be47f2d.mp4?t=1741367325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/5ed3e5ff4d1f6856428a45ec2da871c7.avif?t=1741367325\" width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Myrmidon is a co-op puzzle-platformer inspired by stop-motion animated films. You and your teammate take on the roles of a seasoned animator and his new puppet  in an adventure full of wonders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What do you prefer: pulling off daring acrobatics under the spotlight, or pulling the strings of an imaginary world from behind the scenes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/e4bd3c989043d14c94383ef52e457a26.poster.avif?t=1741367325\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/e4bd3c989043d14c94383ef52e457a26.webm?t=1741367325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/e4bd3c989043d14c94383ef52e457a26.mp4?t=1741367325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the world through two unique perspectives</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE ANIMATOR</strong> moves around the miniature sets of their studio in first-person view. They manipulate the set pieces to clear a path for the puppet.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE PUPPET</strong> traverses the imaginary world inspired by the sets in third-person view. It performs the acrobatic sequences set up by its creator.&quot;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/b0ea0853bcce5a9d5a5878cca15cb876.poster.avif?t=1741367325\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/b0ea0853bcce5a9d5a5878cca15cb876.webm?t=1741367325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/b0ea0853bcce5a9d5a5878cca15cb876.mp4?t=1741367325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Work together to clear obstacles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The various dangers that stand in your way will challenge your ability to communicate with your teammate and synchronize your actions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you  trust your animator and take the leap of faith ? Will you be able to reliably spot your puppet and save it from a deadly fall? <br>  <br><strong>NOTE: This game is co-op only : it requires both players to have an internet connection. Myrmidon does not include any in-game chat features : it is heavily recommended to use an external voice chat software.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/3c742b58292a4482c392138d118fdc2b.poster.avif?t=1741367325\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/3c742b58292a4482c392138d118fdc2b.webm?t=1741367325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247270/extras/3c742b58292a4482c392138d118fdc2b.mp4?t=1741367325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Studio Popote</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Studio Popote is a group of game students based in Valenciennes, France. It was founded in 2024 by Rémi Leroy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The studio is committed in pushing visual story-telling, compelling gameplay elements and show casing the many young talents part of the project. </p>",
